==Bundles==
*Wine is used in the {{Bundle|enchanter||y}}.
*One silver (or better) quality wine is an option for {{bundle|missing||y}}.
*Wine is one of the options for {{bundle|brewers||y}}.

==Tailoring==
Wine can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the [[Tailoring|Black Leather Jacket]].  [[File:Shirt138.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a purple dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
One Wine (of any type) may be requested by [[Blobfish]] in a [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quest]] to increase the capacity of the pond from 5 to 7.

